Added `get_display_verbose_name_plural()`, `get_instance_display_text_content(instance)`, and `get_instance_display_strings(instance)` override hooks to `ViewTestCases.ListObjectsViewTestCase` for test cases whose list view's underlying queryset is over a different model than `self.model`. All three default to the previous hard-coded behavior, so existing test cases need no changes.
Inlined the `update_connected_endpoints` post_save signal and `_create_cable_termination_rows` helper into `Cable.save()` (as `_materialize_initial_terminations()`, `_build_cable_paths_for_terminations()`, and `_sync_cable_path_active_flags()`), so the side effects of saving a Cable are discoverable from the model file. The `raw=True` fixture-loading guard is no longer needed since `loaddata` bypasses `save()`.
